     <div class="block block-block" id="block-block-12">
      <h2>
       Freeform Music Radio
      </h2>
      <div class="content">
       <p>
        Lucky Dog Radio features hand-crafted programs that mix new and old music drawn from all over the universe of sound. Internet radio's antidote to all that's boring and repetitious about terrestrial radio, LDR is where the flame of freeform radio still burns.
       </p>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="block block-block" id="block-block-17">
      <h2>
       LDR Listening Links
      </h2>
      <div class="content">
       <p>
        Give Lucky Dog Radio a listen in iTunes under Internet Radio &gt; Eclectic.
       </p>
       <p>
        You can also listen to LDR via a stand-alone media player by clicking on the icon below that corresponds to your player of choice.
       </p>

       <h2 class="title">
        <a href="/program1327">
         Program #1327
        </a>
       </h2>
       <div class="content">
        <p>
         Here's the complete playist.
        </p>
        <p>
         NELSON RIDDLE ORCHESTRA . . . . . Route 66 Theme (opening theme) . . . . .
         <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00005YU9F?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=luckydogradio-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00005YU9F">
          Route 66 and Other Great TV Themes/More Hit TV Themes
         </a>
         <br/>
         JACK HALEY . . . . . If I Only Had A Heart . . . . .
         <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00000DSCA/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00000DSCA&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=luckydogradio-20&amp;linkId=889f2e21fe78ef018d189734372eb61d" target="_blank">
          Wizard of Oz
         </a>
         <br/>
         BRIAN ENO . . . . . Seven Deadly Finns . . . . .
         <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B000006YHU/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B000006YHU&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=luckydogradio-20&amp;linkId=fd14597954cf1a0a2aab9fe7a947a088" target="_blank">
          Volume II: Vocal
         </a>
         <img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=luckydogradio-20&amp;l=am2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B000006YHU" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1"/>
         <br/>
         THE GOLDBERG SISTERS . . . . . Erik Everhard . . . . .
         <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B004DO4L5Y/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B004DO4L5Y&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=luckydogradio-20&amp;linkId=a1fb0464e427ed0d46af62211fe10acd" target="_blank">
          The Goldberg Sisters
         </a>
         <img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=luckydogradio-20&amp;l=am2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B004DO4L5Y" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1"/>
         <br/>
         ARIEL PINK’S HAUNTED GRAFFITI . . . . . Little Wig . . . . .
         <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B003G7DSI0/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B003G7DSI0&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=luckydogradio-20&amp;linkId=ad0c9bf104dac7ca33d4082af05b3de1" target="_blank">
          Before Today
         </a>
         <img alt="" border="0" height="1" src="//ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=luckydogradio-20&amp;l=am2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B003G7DSI0" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" width="1"/>
         <br/>
         DAVID DEVANT &amp; HIS SPIRIT WIFE . . . . . This Is for Real . . . . .
         <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B002SQK16M/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B002SQK16M&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=luckydogradio-20&amp;linkId=df0f6de54dbc4fde9a4fcb246075d1be" target="_blank">
          Work Lovelife Miscellaneous
         </a>
